pins.title: Neutral Boho Bedroom Decor Ideas
pins.description: Create a serene bedroom with natural textures, neutral colors, and minimalist boho elements. Featuring linen bedding, macrame wall art, and wooden accents.
pins.ai_explanation: Excellent match - perfectly combines boho elements (macrame, natural textures) with minimalist design (clean lines, neutral palette). The room demonstrates restraint typical of minimalism while incorporating bohemian warmth through natural materials.

pins.title: Minimalist Bedroom with Natural Textures
pins.description: Simple bedroom design featuring organic cotton bedding, jute rugs, and carefully curated decor pieces for a calm, uncluttered space.
pins.ai_explanation: Good alignment with the prompt. Strong minimalist foundation with clean white walls and simple furniture. Natural textures (jute, cotton) add subtle boho influences without overwhelming the minimalist aesthetic.

pins.title: Colorful Bohemian Bedroom Design
pins.description: Vibrant boho bedroom with rich jewel tones, patterned textiles, and eclectic furniture pieces for a maximalist bohemian look.
pins.ai_explanation: Poor match - while this is clearly bohemian in style, it completely contradicts the 'minimalist' aspect of the prompt. The room features excessive patterns, bright colors, and cluttered decor that goes against minimalist principles.

pins.title: Sage Green Minimalist Bedroom
pins.description: Peaceful bedroom sanctuary with sage green accents, natural wood elements, and carefully selected boho touches for warmth.
pins.ai_explanation: Strong match - demonstrates perfect balance between minimalist restraint and boho warmth. Sage green adds color without being overwhelming, wood elements provide natural boho texture, and the overall composition remains clean and uncluttered.

pins.title: Modern Industrial Bedroom
pins.description: Contemporary bedroom featuring exposed brick, metal fixtures, and modern furniture for an urban industrial aesthetic.
pins.ai_explanation: Very poor match - this is clearly an industrial style bedroom with no boho or minimalist elements. The exposed brick, metal fixtures, and urban aesthetic are completely different from the warm, natural, minimal boho style requested.

pins.title: Industrial Home Office with Warm Lighting
pins.description: Perfectly balanced industrial office featuring exposed brick, metal desk, Edison bulb lighting, and cozy textile elements for warmth.
pins.ai_explanation: Excellent balance of industrial and cozy elements. The exposed brick and metal furniture provide clear industrial aesthetic, while warm Edison lighting, wooden accents, and soft textiles add the cozy comfort element.

pins.title: Cozy Brick Wall Office Space
pins.description: Home office design combining industrial brick walls with warm wood desk, comfortable seating, and ambient lighting for productivity.
pins.ai_explanation: Outstanding match - perfectly embodies 'cozy industrial'. Brick wall provides strong industrial foundation, while warm wood desk, comfortable chair, and soft lighting create an inviting, cozy workspace atmosphere.

pins.title: Modern Industrial Workspace Design
pins.description: Sleek industrial office with polished concrete floors, steel fixtures, and minimal decor for a clean, modern workspace.
pins.ai_explanation: Insufficient cozy elements - while clearly industrial in style, this space lacks the warmth and comfort suggested by 'cozy'. The polished concrete, steel fixtures, and minimal approach create a cold rather than inviting atmosphere.

pins.title: Rustic Farmhouse Office
pins.description: Charming farmhouse office featuring reclaimed wood, vintage decor, and shabby chic elements for a cozy country workspace.
pins.ai_explanation: Wrong style category - this is clearly farmhouse/rustic style, not industrial. While it achieves the 'cozy' aspect well, it completely lacks industrial elements like metal, brick, or concrete that define the requested aesthetic.

pins.title: Warm Industrial Office Decor
pins.description: Industrial office space softened with warm leather chair, wool rug, and brass accents while maintaining metal and concrete elements.
pins.ai_explanation: Good integration of industrial and cozy elements. Metal shelving and concrete walls provide industrial foundation, while leather furniture, wool textiles, and brass fixtures add warmth and comfort without compromising the industrial aesthetic.
